# Ex. 7 :- Define a function convert_bool_to_binary that receives a boolean and returns 1 if it is true and 0 if it is false.

Examples:

>>> convert_bool_to_binary(True)
1
>>> convert_bool_to_binary(False)
0

Solution :- 

def convert_bool_to_binary(a_boolean):
    if a_boolean:
        return True
    return False
